column2: "With this, the head has been crushed. Now, shall we crush the hands?"
"Sorry we're late! We were still making adjustments!"
"I've got the gist of the situation! I can't believe they'd go this far...!"

"So the Commander has come to meet me
directly. Do you intend to fight with that mechanical doll?"
"Fat chance. That's not what I'm here to do."
